16	/**
17	 * Public blog post — individual article page.
18	 *
19	 * Renders any Upload with `publishedAt IS NOT NULL AND slug = :slug`.
20	 * Unpublished uploads 404 (instead of leaking existence via an auth
21	 * redirect). Because the same underlying Upload row powers the private
