74	    // Soft-deleted posts 404 rather than render, so a shared link for
75	    // a retracted post behaves the same as an unknown slug. The
76	    // `visibility: "org"` filter excludes both "private" (uploader-
77	    // only) and "semi-private" (firm-only) rows; by construction
78	    // these shouldn't coexist with a publish state, but enforcing it
79	    // here guarantees that even a stale slug cached in a post's URL
